    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
